Polymetal Jumps Most in Week as Second-Quarter Revenue Gains

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-07-25T15:56:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/polymetal-jumps-most-in-week-russian-silver-miner-revenue-rises.html
OAO Polymetal jumped the most in a
week after the Russian silver and gold producer reported a 26
percent increase in second-quarter revenue to $315 million
compared with the same period last year.  The shares climbed 1.2 percent to 563.9 rubles by the 6:45
p.m. close in Moscow, its biggest gain since July 18.  Silver production fell 27 percent in the period to 4.3
million ounces, while gold output retreated 16 percent to 94,000
ounces, Polymetal said in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
